  <refnamediv>
    <refname>lfsr_init</refname>
    <refpurpose>Initialize a LFSR register object</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>


<refsynopsisdiv>
   <title>Calling Sequence</title>
   <synopsis>
   lfsr = lfsr_init(deg)
   
   </synopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsection>
   <title>Parameters</title>
   <variablelist>
   <varlistentry><term>deg:</term>
      <listitem><para> LFSR polynomial degree (from 0 to 15)</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   <varlistentry><term>lfsr:</term>
      <listitem><para> Resulting LFSR object (can be used with the function lfsr_process)</para></listitem></varlistentry>
   </variablelist>
</refsection>

<refsection>
   <title>Description</title>
   <para>
<para>The LFSR register size will be 1 + degree,
and the polynomial choosen so as to have the longest minimal sequence.</para>
   </para>
   <para>
</para>
</refsection>

